message.raw:
Cosmetic logging changes:
* Prefix log lines with [autoscrub:<severity_level>] and [ffmpeg:<filter_name>]
* [ffmpeg:silence_detect] progress overwrites last line with end='\r' of print
* Overwrite "100% complete [00:00:00 remaining]" with time taken and avg. speed
* Ensure progress percentage doesn't exceed 100.
